{
  "id": "adv_event_2406_02_03",
  "title": "トリエル_マネージャーさんへ.mov",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_yu-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "動画とはいえ、{user}さんが\n目の前におると思うと、めっちゃ恥ずかしいわぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even though it's just a video‚\nit’s super embarrassing thinking that {user}-san’s right in front of me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 7.9272562027,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_yu-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "あんま見やんといて\nそんなじっと見られたら、うち困ります……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t look at me too much.\nIf you keep staring at me like that‚ I’ll be troubled…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.1333333333,
      "endTime": 14.7284812292,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_yu-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "ふふふ、冗談はこれくらいにして本題に入らなな\nうちだけ尺が延びたら怒られてまうわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚ I should stop joking around and get to the main point.\nIf only my part is long‚ I’ll get scolded.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.9333337784,
      "endTime": 23.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_yu-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、いつもホンマにおおきに\nうち知ってるんよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ thank you so much.\nI know everything.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.9333341599,
      "endTime": 29.990250206,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_yu-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "みんなのために沢山営業かけて、スケジュール組んで\n時にはよそで嫌なこと言われても頭下げて――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re running around doing a lot of business for everyone‚ arranging schedules‚\nand sometimes even lowering your head and taking abuse from others――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.2000008266,
      "endTime": 38.800000000000004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_yu-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "でも事務所ではしんどい顔いっこも見せへん\n{user}さん、かっこ良過ぎますわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but you never show any signs of hardship at the office.\n{user}-san‚ you’re too cool.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.0333400091,
      "endTime": 46.1778271993,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_yu-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "そんな{user}さんに大事にしてもらえて\nうちらはホンマ幸せもんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We're truly blessed to be cherished\nby someone like you‚ {user}-san",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.3666707993,
      "endTime": 52.5000022888,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_yu-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "みんなおる前やと恥ずかしくて、なかなか\n言われへんから、この機会に伝えさせてもらいました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s embarrassing to say it in front of everyone‚\nso I’ll take this opportunity to tell you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.8000026067,
      "endTime": 60.3542655309,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_yu-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ……これ以上語ったらうちが泣けてまうし\nこれくらいにしとかなな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu… I should stop here\nbefore I start crying.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.5666692734,
      "endTime": 68.47426567080001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_yu-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "ほなほな～やで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Bye bye‚ then!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.6666692734,
      "endTime": 70.6810755253,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_rui-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、こんにちは\n天動瑠依です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ hello.\nI’m Rui Tendo.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.881078577,
      "endTime": 76.80026211730001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_rui-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "初めは優とすみれに手伝ってもらおうと\n思ったんですけど、今回は一人で頑張ろうと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "At first‚ I was thinking of having Yu and Sumire help me out‚\nbut this time I’m going to do my best on my own.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.0335954665,
      "endTime": 83.6145250319,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_rui-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんに伝えたいことは\n沢山あるんですけど、改めてカメラを前にすると――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There are a lot of things I want to tell you‚ {user}-san‚\nbut once I’m in front of the camera again――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.8345244089,
      "endTime": 90.84774524369999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_rui-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "なんだか恥ずかしいですね……\n落ち着いて、用意した台本通りに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "it’s kind of embarrassing…\nCalm down‚ and just follow the script…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.0821889559,
      "endTime": 98.2557264963,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_rui-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "まずは、いつもトリエルをマネジメントしていただき\n本当にありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "First of all‚ thank you very much\nfor always managing TRINITYAiLE.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.449059677,
      "endTime": 104.7144135315,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_rui-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんに出会わなければ、今の\nトリエルはあり得なかった訳ですし感謝しかありません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I hadn’t met {user}-san‚\nthe current TRINITYAiLE wouldn’t exist. I’m filled with nothing but gratitude.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.9412888209,
      "endTime": 111.61448589960001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_rui-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "あとはそうですね。{user}さんから見て\n……私って、どうでしょうか……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And then‚ well. From your perspective‚ {user}-san…\n…what do you think of me…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.8211527188,
      "endTime": 119.9144120375,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_rui-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "あっ！　どうっていうのはその、変な意味ではなくて！\nもちろんアイドルとしてどうか、というお話です！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah! I don’t mean that in a weird way!\nOf course‚ I’m asking what you think of me as an idol!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.181493473,
      "endTime": 127.82215118410001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_rui-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "意外とそういう真に迫ったお話を\nしたことがないなって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s surprising that we’ve never\nhad such a serious conversation before…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.0354842503,
      "endTime": 132.68038199729997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_rui-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "こ、今度、ぜひ聞かせて下さいね。私がスケジュールを\n押さえておきますから！　それでは、失礼します！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ please let me know sometime!\nI’ll keep my schedule open! Well then‚ excuse me!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.8670486926,
      "endTime": 141.0848944187,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_smr-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、お疲れ様です\nTRINITYAiLEの奥山すみれです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ good work.\nI’m Sumire Okuyama from TRINITYAiLE!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.3848883151,
      "endTime": 149.0508746623,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_smr-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "今日は{user}さんに\n沢山『ありがとう』を伝えようと思います！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Today‚ I’m going to tell you\n“thank you” a bunch!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.2515549818,
      "endTime": 153.9522350469,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_smr-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんは、毎日夜遅くまで事務所で\nお仕事してるのに東京駅まで送り迎えしてくれたり――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even though {user}-san works at the office late every night‚\nyou still pick me up and drop me off at Tokyo Station――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.1515549818,
      "endTime": 162.4266798178,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_smr-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "学校の宿題の相談にも乗ってくれたり\nいつも見守ってくれて、とっても感謝してます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and you even help me with my school homework‚\nI’m so grateful that you’re always watching over me!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.6182216484,
      "endTime": 169.5581991035,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_smr-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "それに、もう一度演技のお仕事にチャレンジ\nする時なんて、優しく背中を押してくれて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And when I decided to challenge myself with acting again‚\nyou gently gave me a push…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 169.7515549818,
      "endTime": 177.1493781248,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_smr-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "共演者さんのことや自分の演技に不安になっても\n一番近くで応援してくれましたよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even when I was anxious about my co-stars and my acting‚\nyou were by my side to cheer me on‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 177.3515549818,
      "endTime": 184.94069329890002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_smr-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "私、すっごくすっごく嬉しかったです\n{user}さんが応援してくれると……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was so‚ so happy.\nWhen {user}-san cheers me on…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 185.1515549818,
      "endTime": 192.7619403997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_smr-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "心がじんわりーって温かくなるんです！\n実家のおこた以上の温もりです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "my heart feels all warm and fuzzy!\nIt’s warmer than the kotatsu at my parents’ house!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 192.8182168166,
      "endTime": 200.4118211905,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
